H3.text: Who was elected US President in November 2012. OBAMA

A4.text: On November 6, 2012, Obama won 332 electoral votes, exceeding the 270 required for him to be reelected as president.

A5.text: Obama defeated Republican opponent Mitt Romney and his running mate Paul Ryan in the 2012 presidential election.
